{"tid":1485544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一日未證實到係鬼 一日我都唔撚割呀!","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:21:10.000Z","uid":154224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2db3fcc262c07d30e08411fcc588ad07fb87bd","tid":1485544,"uid":154224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:11:09.000Z","msg":"我知有鬼呀屌<br />\n我都知有人留守可能會破壞左今日和平遊行<br />\n但係只要有一個係真手足我就唔撚割呀!<br />\n<br />\n仲係前線果班你地聽撚住呀<br />\n我希望你地要以大局為重 今晚撤退<br />\n同時我希望其他已經走左既人都以大局為重 永不割蓆 唔屌其他手足<br />\n同我記撚住呀!!!"},{"pid":"646a2d3b795a8f98df141d8b0252a67ceceafa76","tid":1485544,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆 不分化 核爆都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"2b088a9905e33a27d3199bcd614c34ae1dbdbd9f","tid":1485544,"uid":227981,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">據連登post，好多好多真。前線都已經be water返屋企了。<br />\n我相信剩低果班應該都係狗？<br />\n話晒今日冇乜警犬出動。<br />\n我地就睇下成班戲子今晚點收科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者朋友可以映低班狗做記錄，第二日又可以4點質問警犬。<br />\n要做得好好睇睇呀，最少發一百粒彈</span>"},{"pid":"1197b3e1b25ff26b5c07afaef25b9036901619c5","tid":1485544,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"致分化撚，割乜春蓆，170萬人出黎skip左唔計？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485352</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6cc9196721f4c552fa8f63dabe34532367826913","tid":1485544,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/wwLBxU5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwLBxU5.png&h=6f29b2d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f250d80af095d5c5e6d8ed4684a0bdc32ee0446f","tid":1485544,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"前線唔係鬼 佢地係手足呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4981445df462cae18d4bb4b879b4ac639bbf5a0f","tid":1485544,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"5970f12f7ee566f92a308347b3d36e7c34fab738","tid":1485544,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔割，但希望大家淋完雨好返屋企沖涼喇，做嘢要目標為本<br />\n現場手足如果勸完都唔走就自己走啦，佢地見冇人都會走<br />\n<br />\n停止捉鬼，由得啲鬼自己OT啦"},{"pid":"9f1225b3aa51a44b69c274e6d0a292f283b5fa04","tid":1485544,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"有冇金鐘現場手足話我聽發生咩事？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1483916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1483916</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家幫手推到金鐘現場手足應我</span></span><br />\n<br />\n叫人走絕對冇問題<br />\n抬佢走都冇所謂<br />\n但係請記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">千祈唔好捉鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日捉鬼捉到咁開心<br />\n下次升級嘅時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">班真鬼就以捉鬼為理由將我哋啲手足捉上警車</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你地班五毛<br />\n幾時話割蓆？<br />\n叫人走就係割蓆？<br />\n今日d PO到11點為止都非常正常<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇啦啦會有一班人將今日勸前線走既說話扭曲成係割蓆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">極懷疑開PO屌分化果d先係五毛</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecb11b9ade1257b6fc0c017b5cafd81ee0e5689d","tid":1485544,"uid":154224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!"}]}